# Emphasize R
*.R linguist-detectable
*.Rmd linguist-language=R

# De-emphasize non-code files
*.txt linguist-documentation
*.pdf linguist-documentation
*.da linguist-documentation
*.sas linguist-documentation
*.sps linguist-documentation
*.do linguist-documentation
*.dct linguist-documentation
*.html linguist-documentation
*.ipynb linguist-documentation
